k mempedulikan ancaman ke bentengnya dan memilih melanjutkan serangan utama ke sayap raja.} 19. Nc5 Qxc7 20. Ne6 {And White begin to harvest Black pieces because of his ignorance. Beside a Knight fork both the Black Rook and Queen also being attacked by other piece.  Dan Putih mulai memanen buah hitam, selain di garpu oleh kuda, masing-masing ratu dan benteng hitam juga diserang buah lain.} Qf7 {Not much choice to retreat } 21. Bxb5 gxf3 22. Ng5 fxg2 23. Rf2 {White is still not save to take the free Queen.} Bg4 {Black is on berserk mode and trying to activated another arsenal into battlefield. But after White Queen retreated it is clear that the Black Queen is trap. Correct will be 23..Nxe4!  Yang benar adalah 23..Nxe4. Dengan berambisi mengikutsertakan gajah hitam ke medan pertempuran, ratu hitam betul2 terperangkap.} 24. Qb3 Rfc8 25. Rfc2 Rxc2 26. Rxc2 Nh4 {Now the Queen had been sacrificed, Black only get more tempo to mate the King for compensation, but it is a promising attack?  } 27. Nxf7 Kxf7 {Black losing important tempo by recapture the Knight here. Much more still fighting here is 27.. Nf3+ 28. Kxg2 Nd4 29. Qc4 f3+ 30. Kg3 Kxf7 31. Rd2 Nxb5 32.Qxb5. At this point Friso is about 5 minutes left.} 28. Rc7+ {Now White is a Queen up, but Anish still spend some times thinking the best deadly move. Here 28.d4+ is more deadly because it is open a diagonal to the Queen } Kg6 29. h3 f3 {Nf3+ 30. Kxg2 Nd4 31. Qc4 Bf3+ 32. Kg1 Bxe4 } 30. Be1 {A natural defence and Black is practically losing now.} Bh6 31. Bxh4 Rxa2 32. Qxa2 Be3+ 33. Bf2 Bxf2+ 34. Kxf2 Nxe4+ 35. Kg1 Ng5 36. Bd3+ Kf6 37. Rxh7 {The only Black hope to counter attack by Nxh3 is dismissed. White is a Queen up so it's time to resign. } 